msgid ""
"The calendar app takes is the best way to have full control over your "
"site events."
msgstr ""
"La aplicación calendario toma la mejor forma de tener un control completo"
" sobre los eventos del sitio."

#: ../apps/calendar/index.rst:19
msgid "The calendar month view"
msgstr "La vista mensual del calendario"

#: ../apps/calendar/index.rst:21
msgid ""
"It shows all the events for this month, but you can navigate through the "
"months. You can switch also to Week and day views. Clicking on the "
"calendar will allow you to add new events."
msgstr ""
